    "title": {
      "rendered": "7 Unique Fundraising Tools for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-15852\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"7 Unique Fundraising Tools for Nonprofits\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/7-Unique-Fundraising-Tools-for-Nonprofits.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>In <em><strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\">Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</a></strong>,</em> a 40-hour work for a new media manager is outlined with five hours allotted weekly to experimenting with new online and mobile fundraising tools. The seven listed below are just the tip of the iceberg\u00a0\u2013\u00a0and most of them are still in beta.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Having just celebrated the <a href=\"http://www.pewinternet.org/packages/the-web-at-25/\">25th Anniversary of the World Wide Web</a>, the nonprofit sector now has a wide array of amazing new fundraising tools at our fingertips that we couldn&#8217;t have imagined just a decade ago. However, unless your nonprofit has allocated the time and resources necessary to be an early adopter, your nonprofit will struggle to take advantage of this next generation of online and mobile fundraising tools.</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Face the Planet<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/\">facetheplanet.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Face the Planet enables users to hypothetically purchase real estate ($3-4 per landmark) and 85% of the proceeds are donated to environmental and wildlife conservation organizations.\u00a0Watch this one! More gaming, geolocation, and social functionality to be added soon.\u00a0<strong>And if your nonprofit is working to conserve the planet and its wild inhabitants,</strong> <a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/aboutus\">contact the founder directly</a> to see about having your nonprofit listed.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15821\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Face the Planet\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet.png?resize=600%2C342\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Purchase properties and select the nonprofit to benefit:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15820\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Face the Planet 2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet-2.png?resize=600%2C395\" width=\"600\" height=\"395\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet-2.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Face-the-Planet-2.png?resize=300%2C197&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>You are then attached to the property and added to a map:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/map\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15827\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"tower grove park\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tower-grove-park.png?resize=600%2C346\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tower-grove-park.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tower-grove-park.png?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>And you earn badges and property certificates:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/map\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15823\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"badges\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/badges.png?resize=600%2C210\" width=\"600\" height=\"210\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/badges.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/badges.png?resize=300%2C105&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.facetheplanet.com/map\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15824\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"my properties\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/my-properties.png?resize=600%2C240\" width=\"600\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/my-properties.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/my-properties.png?resize=300%2C120&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Wizeo<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wizeo.org\">wizeo.org</a></h2>\n<p>Wizeo is an online platform where members can bid to have one-on-one 15-minute video chats or donate to attend a group video chat with participating thought leaders and celebrities.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.wizeo.org\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15837\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Wizeo\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Wizeo.png?resize=600%2C346\" width=\"600\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Wizeo.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Wizeo.png?resize=300%2C173&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. Guilty Pledgers<br />\n<a href=\"https://guiltypledgers.com\">guiltypledgers.com</a></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Guilty Pledgers is a mobile app launched by <a href=\"https://www.spotify.com\">Spotify</a> that enables users to create fundraising parties where guests can pledge money to add their favorite songs to the party playlist.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://guiltypledgers.com\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15834\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"guilty pledgers\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/guilty-pledgers.png?resize=600%2C283\" width=\"600\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/guilty-pledgers.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/guilty-pledgers.png?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. Ink to the People<br />\n<a href=\"http://inktothepeople.com/\">inktothepeople.com</a></h2>\n<p>Ink to the People empowers anyone to create and sell their own t-shirt designs to benefit their favorite nonprofits.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://inktothepeople.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15839\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"tshirt fundraiser\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tshirt-fundraiser.png?resize=600%2C311\" width=\"600\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tshirt-fundraiser.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/tshirt-fundraiser.png?resize=300%2C155&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Fundography<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fundography.com/\">fundography.com</a></h2>\n<p>Fundography allows event attendees to upload and share photos taken at the event and then event attendees can purchase the photos for $2 each\u00a0to benefit their favorite nonprofit.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.fundography.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-15845\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"fundography\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/fundography.png?resize=600%2C316\" width=\"600\" height=\"316\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/fundography.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/fundography.png?resize=300%2C158&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. GiveMob<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.givemobapp.org/\">givemobapp.org</a></h2>\n<p>GiveMob is a mobile app that allows users to donate to select nonprofits via text with just a couple of taps.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.givemobapp.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15842\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"GiveMob\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/GiveMob.png?resize=600%2C342\" width=\"600\" height=\"342\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/GiveMob.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/GiveMob.png?resize=300%2C171&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>7. Cause Direct<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.causepayments.com\">causepayments.com</a><br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Cause Direct enables businesses to donate to their favorite charity or school every time they accept a credit or debit card payment.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.causepayments.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-15818\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Cause Direct\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Cause-Direct.png?resize=600%2C312\" width=\"600\" height=\"312\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Cause-Direct.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/Cause-Direct.png?resize=300%2C156&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignleft  wp-image-16024\" style=\"margin: 10px; border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"mobile for good look inside\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/mobile-for-good-look-inside.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media,\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a>\u00a0is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.<br />\n<strong>\u00a0</strong></p>\n",
